title: Trendsperado 9/1: Anna's Streaming Corner, NBA, Stacey Dash, Mississippi, Lukoil, Mary Peltola
itunes:title: Trendsperado 9/1: Anna's Streaming Corner, NBA, Stacey Dash, Mississippi, Lukoil, Mary Peltola
description:
In this edition of Trendsperado, Jack and Miles are joined by Anna Hossnieh for a special "Anna's Streaming Corner" and then they discuss NBA news, Stacey Dash "clueless" that DMX died, Mississippi pledging to tax Biden's student debt money, a Russian oil exec dying under mysterious (defenestrate-y) circumstances, and Sarah Palin losing Alaska's special election to Mary Peltola!
